{"tid":690024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【電台】有冇人聽903大？","createTime":"2018-06-04T13:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T16:29:51.000Z","uid":149371,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2a36f9ec900aa14cf90b936a7ebc0527db0cfadd","tid":690024,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"小學5、6年級開始聽，邊做功課邊聽。一至五好似係「架勢堂」。星期六晚會聽到深夜，「森美移動」、「午夜閒談」（鄒凱光、余迪偉、有耳非文）當然係係床度用耳機聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。好似仲有個節叫「妹妹妹妹」。<br />\n<br />\n中學時期一放學就手機開FM，聽住搭車番屋企。艾粒（唔記得節目名，do姐未加入之前），節目尾半個鐘有廣播劇，一至五好似日日唔同，大連的子民、黃鳯女士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、末日輝、文化節拍，仲有日係學友與jimmy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。之後就細so「好回家」，聽住歌做功課。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰陣番學會同同學傾啲節目，最新嘅廣東歌都係咁接收到。之後出智能手機就少咗聽。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a2a2d5a64d2280511ba77ad87746949dda4e7d","tid":690024,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"而家開903網聽緊梁文禮，播住歌、又講吓64晚會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cb04543e73af1c54a9357183e1ee88d676950b","tid":690024,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"有啲掛住中學嘅日子，明明當時好想快啲畢業入大學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2e4540bf347beb2a57b7f6a14ca6a1c3590d15","tid":690024,"uid":126502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"Ching 既經歷同我一樣，相信好多90後都係咁"},{"pid":"436d477c9b8492152410cb650ef0ab67e36a2005","tid":690024,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"禮拜六晚聽 遮時打令"},{"pid":"871f2c0283d8ec80929a2b03f21fd1ede0c93025","tid":690024,"uid":94739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"萬世巨星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16d3c3757676c19d1eada92a98f6249394b67df","tid":690024,"uid":158477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"樓主講個D都有聽 以前返學時期真係攬住收音機訓<br />\n森美移動(最記得有笑談廣東話同廣播劇街車王) 架勢堂又係經典 <br />\n妹妹妹妹聽E記<br />\n艾粒個個應該係萬世巨星?<br />\n仲有短期租約Wasabi<br />\n再耐D仲有嘩嘩嘩打到黎 應該係我第一個聽嘅電台節目"},{"pid":"964d59b4dfc7ab27c1becf8aff5a60cdf14b0b35","tid":690024,"uid":39315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"由森美小儀dot dot dot聽 果時仲有嘩嘩嘩打到黎<br />\n之後再聽萬世巨星"},{"pid":"eba3fb92598972c8b2351f24ee76c43eaf409ee0","tid":690024,"uid":179120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"1872"},{"pid":"33592ff299d05d0339520dbe797a9e138ec7cefc","tid":690024,"uid":6992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"喪Do男"},{"pid":"04f41f5e8487109ccafa768aefee3f4d9182a174","tid":690024,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"森美移動有出過歌，小學雞嗰陣聽覺得佢地幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有同薛凱琪嘅廣播劇。"},{"pid":"ac0a59127ee2748d40e7cb2b2e11fa0bd515d8ad","tid":690024,"uid":39531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"喪do男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e8e328e68237b16cb06f2034906dd4c6679b28","tid":690024,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac0a59127ee2748d40e7cb2b2e11fa0bd515d8ad","tid":690024,"uid":39531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"喪do男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm